name: Rec Room
summary: Rec Room is the best place to play, create, and connect with people from all over the world. Whether you’re here to socialize, compete, or just chill, there’s always something new to do. Explore MILLIONS of unique player-made rooms or jump into Rec Room Originals like Paintball, Dodgeball, Golden Trophy, Isle of Lost Skulls & more! Rec Room is free to play, easy to join, and cross-platform on everything from phones to VR headsets!
